A Hardy gout tuber is obtained during the My Arm's Big Adventure quest from Murcaily. They can not be dug up or planted in a herb patch. One is given to the player after reaching 60% favour in Tai Bwo Wannai Cleanup, but is immediately replaced a handful of hardy gout tubers by Murcaily after My Arm goes on a rampage.
